                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-647-18350202 t18350202-647-punishment-134"></join>Con<lb></lb>fined Twelve Months.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Second Jury, before Mr. Sergeant Arabin</hi>.</p>
